==============
The O-Kay-Blog
==============

What's this?
------------

The O-Kay-Blog is blogging system written using the Kay Framework to run on Google App Engine. 
It is a clone of the Bloggart blog system by Nick Johnson http://github.com/Arachnid/bloggart
http://blog.notdot.net/2009/10/Writing-a-blog-system-on-App-Engine

To run this on Google App Engine, make the necessary changes in the following files:
- app.yaml
	- Change my-appid to your own Google App Engine appid
- blog/config.py
	- Change host from my-appid.appspot.com to your own host name.
	- Change the other settings to customize your blog.